<p>Hi,</p>

<p>
  We received your request to change your TheraSaurus plan.
  <% if @effective_at %>
    The change will take effect on
    <strong><%= l @effective_at.to_date, format: :long %></strong>
    (the end of your current billing period).
  <% else %>
    The change will take effect at the end of your current billing
    period.
  <% end %>
</p>

<p>
  Until then, your current plan stays active and nothing changes for
  you. There are no proration charges or refunds —
  <% if @new_amount_label %>
    the new
    <strong><%= @new_amount_label %></strong>
    rate will simply replace your current plan at renewal.
  <% else %>
    the new rate will simply replace your current plan at renewal.
  <% end %>
</p>

<p>
  Changed your mind? You can cancel the scheduled change any time before
  it takes effect from your
  <%= link_to "Membership settings", membership_url %>
  → Manage subscription.
</p>

<p>Thanks,<br>The TheraSaurus team</p>
